fr.upem.jShell.JShellServer

Class ExerciseManagerVerticle

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractVerticle
      • fr.upem.jShell.JShellServer.ExerciseManagerVerticle

  • public class ExerciseManagerVerticle
extends AbstractVerticle
    Retrieves, stores and provides the exercises required by the clients. Moreover, it receives the requests for evaluating an exercise and delegate the evaluations with the correct tests.
    Author:
    mattia
